markdown: KAYMICH III - PRINT/INK TYPE, COLOR/PAPER TYPE/ MENTHOL LOAD TEST VARIABLES: PRINT - DIAMOND OR SALEM GOLD LOGOS INK - GREEN OR GOLD PAPERS - REF. 856, REF. 456, REF. 856 HV, 856 AQUAPEL, 45 G CACO, FILLER PAPER, ZZ PAPER 50 G MG(OH)₂ WITH KCL MENTHOL LOADS - .12% OR .32% TEST ACCOMPLISHED WITH SIX 2 X 2 DESIGNS - 24 PARTS ■ ALL PARTS RAN IN SPC ■ ALL PARTS PACKAGED IMMEDIATELY OFF MAKER/TIPPER (WITHIN 15 MINUTES) ■ ALL TEST LEGS WITHIN EACH 2 X 2 WERE NOT SIGNIFICANTLY DIFFERENT* IN TOBACCO AND SMOKE ANALYSES ■ OBVIOUS ANALYTICAL SMOKE DIFFERENCES WERE PRESENT BETWEEN DESIGNS OF DIFFERING PAPER TYPE ■ TWO TRENDS EXISTED 1. MENTHOL LOAD FROM KAYMICH TRENDED LOW 2. FILTER MENTHOL FROM KAYMICH TRENDED HIGH ■ SED DISCRIMINATION OF INTERNATIONAL PRODUCTS AND SALEM GOLD PROTOTYPES WERE NOT SIGNIFICANTLY DIFFERENT. SALEM BOX PROTOTYPES WERE DIFFERENT. THESE WERE SUBMITTED FOR QDA ANALYSIS. ■ SED DIAGNOSTIC ANALYSES OF SALEM BOX PRODUCTS INDICATED NO PERCEPTUAL TASTE DIFFERENCES. VISUAL DIFFERENCES IN PRINT COLOR, ONLY. 51335 8998
